{"tid":1226124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安全上網, tor教學(有錯請指正)","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:58:04.000Z","uid":244509,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f129d626a511324f13f40c97c1987720bea1970","tid":1226124,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"下載link請參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n本人非it從業員, 以下資訊純屬個人理解, 有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\n據我了解, tor連接分三層(node), 每個node都係一部電腦<br />\n<br />\n你部機 &gt; enter node &gt; relay node &gt; exit node &gt; 你想去既網站<br />\n個網站收到你既browser request(去程)會send番d資料去你部機(回程), 同樣經過上面三層, 不過d node(電腦)會轉, 唔會用番同一部電腦, 確保匿名性<br />\n<br />\n由你部機出既request 會經過tor加密, router, 中間d node睇唔到你send咩data, send去邊個網, 只有exit node 先知, 假設網站使用https, exit node只睇到hostname, 唔會睇到full address.<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 某網購網站<br />\nhostname:<br />\n<a href=\"http://buysomething.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuysomething.com&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=a6531157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://buysomething.com</a><br />\nfull address:<br />\n<a href=\"http://buysomething.com/dangerous_itemA.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuysomething.com%2Fdangerous_itemA.html&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b620f4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://buysomething.com/dangerous_itemA.html</a><br />\n<br />\n如果網站使用https, exit node 只睇到(<a href=\"https://buysomething.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuysomething.com&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=4ff6dc91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buysomething.com</a>), 睇唔到full address(<a href=\"http://buysomething.com/dangerous_itemA.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuysomething.com%2Fdangerous_itemA.html&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b620f4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://buysomething.com/dangerous_itemA.html</a>), 咁就唔知你想買咩/講過咩<br />\n<br />\n其實單靠https , isp, router都只係睇到hostname, 問題係當政府要求網站提供server log, 再問isp拎同一時段客戶ip address check, 咁就搵到你(gg)<br />\n<br />\n連登hash咗個登記email無意思, 純綷防hacker爆格, 如果政府一攞連登同isp ip log同樣玩完<br />\n<br />\n大家要安全應該用tor既forum, 例如 8ch 香港政治台:<br />\n<a href=\"http://oxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion/hkpol/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion%2Fhkpol%2Findex.html&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=1781c611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://oxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion/hkpol/index.html</a><br />\nserver log只有tor exit node既ip, 唔會有你既ip, 亦唔需要email登記, 100%匿名<br />\n<br />\n至於tor俾人破解係需要enter node同exit node由同一人控制, 透過傳送data 既packet size同time delay去match番邊個人send web request去邊個網, enter node知你真ip, exit node知你想去既網站, 之後政府跟番上面程序, 問網站同isp攞ip log就搵到你<br />\n<br />\n針對e個問題, tor改善咗選取exit node既algorithm, 令到冇咁易俾人操控(刻意成為某網站exit node), 但都要個網站更新番個新版tor address先用到新algorithm<br />\ne度講緊既係用tor address既網站, 如8ch 香港政治台. 連登並唔係用tor address, 所以唔清楚exit node點簡<br />\n<br />\n建議大家想簡單了解tor同https既安全性, 一定要去以下網址, 有得互動方式睇下唔同情況下有咩保障:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eff.org/pages/tor-and-https\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eff.org%2Fpages%2Ftor-and-https&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=0f0abc37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eff.org/pages/tor-and-https</a><br />\n<br />\n另外, https安唔安全要睇implementation方式, 用國產手機食得屎<br />\n<br />\n最後呼籲, 如果要安全, 請用8ch 香港政治台:<br />\n<a href=\"http://oxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion/hkpol/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion%2Fhkpol%2Findex.html&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=1781c611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://oxwugzccvk3dk6tj.onion/hkpol/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7af7923f0f66e5688dbf370788dd36d4e3020ba","tid":1226124,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729c371936b07b4a8102f4e0a84a2c5c416afbdb","tid":1226124,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"94a627b7445f6f911bb87decf99af6aef53fb74c","tid":1226124,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"729c371936b07b4a8102f4e0a84a2c5c416afbdb","tid":1226124,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223188/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"去呢度集中補充 GOGOGO"},{"pid":"b70142b14d4020cec4c8f68a343f44839f658b27","tid":1226124,"uid":187714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"電腦白痴 睇完都係唔明<br />\n利申用緊 Samsung C8"},{"pid":"dd4cf4ffbd57fe9521c93bc9c0d5e7f387d38cc3","tid":1226124,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最終目標：完全撤回送中惡法。釋放義士。<br />\n<br />\n暫你老母緩呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗我地仲未打贏，唔好掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行。  星期一出去集會。<br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"63fc6ae8646e665cdd1106217c394a9a0f07cb0f","tid":1226124,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b70142b14d4020cec4c8f68a343f44839f658b27","tid":1226124,"uid":187714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0